description: This API is in preview release for Amazon Connect and is subject to change. To request access to this API, contact Amazon Web ServicesSupport. Provides summary information about the authentication profiles in a specified Amazon Connect instance.

parameters.name: InstanceId
parameters.description: The identifier of the Amazon Connect instance. You can find the instance ID in the Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the instance.

nested_items.name: AuthenticationProfileSummaryList
nested_items.description: A summary of a given authentication profile.

nested_items.name: Id
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of the authentication profile.

nested_items.name: Arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the authentication profile summary.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: The name of the authentication profile summary.

nested_items.name: IsDefault
nested_items.description: Shows whether the authentication profile is the default authentication profile for the Amazon Connect instance. The default authentication profile applies to all agents in an Amazon Connect instance, unless overridden by another authentication profile.

nested_items.name: LastModifiedTime
nested_items.description: The timestamp when the authentication profile summary was last modified.

nested_items.name: LastModifiedRegion
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services Region when the authentication profile summary was last modified.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If there are additional results, this is the token for the next set of results.
